{"tid":2372871,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"拜登的亞洲外交幕僚一字排開，猶如歐巴馬時期的同學會","createTime":"2021-01-20T04:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T04:55:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1873f1d8b44523d2bbb349ff6a334018fa8475c2","tid":2372871,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"隨著1月20日美國繼任總統拜登（Joe Biden）就職典禮逐漸接近，越來越多幕僚名單逐漸浮出水面。其中，由於近年亞太事務重要性逐漸提高，因此坎貝爾（Kurt Campell）、羅森伯格（Laura Rosenberger）、艾莉森（Graham Alison）三人的提名受到極大的關注。<br />\n<br />\n首先，拜登提名前亞太助卿坎貝爾為印太事務協調官（Asia Tsar），而此職位為此次白宮新設立的職位之一，主管中國、台灣事務。<br />\n<br />\n坎貝爾曾任歐巴馬（Barack Obama）時期亞太助卿，同時也是當年歐巴馬「重返亞洲」戰略推動者之一。上任前他則領導顧問公司「亞洲集團」（Asia Group）和創辦智庫「新美國安全中心」(Center for a New American Security）。而這個新設立的職位，也可以看出拜登政府重視亞太事務的態度。<br />\n<br />\n坎貝爾曾在多個公開場合及平台表達對於亞太地區局勢、和美國未來對此區域的相關政策。他曾在頂尖期刊《外交事務》上發表文章表示，文中表示，美國應該要「認真」參與亞太事務，建立聯盟和夥伴關係，以面對中國的威脅和維護現有的秩序。並且，他也贊成美國對台灣的堅定支持。<br />\n<br />\n同時，在去（2020）年12月的「美日台三邊印太安全對話」也表達了現今局勢的看法。他表示，儘管川普執政時退出許多國際組織和其他作為，使得外界對於美國世界領導地位開始產生質疑聲浪，但在拜登執政後，美國將會重新扮演「世界領導」的角色，讓外界知道美國力量「American Power」。<br />\n<br />\n對中問題上，他希望採取「戰略性交往」（Strategic Engagement）。他表示美、中在高科技上的競爭仍會持續。但在氣候變遷、新冠疫情、朝鮮半島議題上，美中該適度合作解決問題。然而，對於兩岸關係上，他則是希望目前緊張情勢能夠逐漸降溫，雙方應該恢復一定程度的對話。<br />\n<br />\n坎貝爾曾在與我駐美大使蕭美琴一起的會議上說：「美國友台，但不反中。」同時，他表示，此議題並非美國所能處理，更何況北京目前握有主動權⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/146198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F146198&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmejQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e2db789c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/146198</a>"},{"pid":"1c7f7902b473824d7f26bce7fee0123639fd09f2","tid":2372871,"uid":270506,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"Third Obama Administration 2021-2024"},{"pid":"ed43e3bd62dbd201c6a47f5995a81e80e6483587","tid":2372871,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"中美和好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/a45a4578b3b2a09d5740bfdc08451d00@1200x1200.jpg?url=https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/10/GettyImages-489974606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fa45a4578b3b2a09d5740bfdc08451d00%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FGettyImages-489974606.jpg&h=17c637be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3c316018c1d09479e4d81775905b763e3a1b2da","tid":2372871,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"溝通，對話，交流，表示關注<br />\n<br />\n嚟嚟去去咪三督屎尿屁"},{"pid":"c4ea664e7dc323ed03fe243c9fdafce2363faca3","tid":2372871,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed43e3bd62dbd201c6a47f5995a81e80e6483587","tid":2372871,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"中美和好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/a45a4578b3b2a09d5740bfdc08451d00@1200x1200.jpg?url=https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/10/GettyImages-489974606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fa45a4578b3b2a09d5740bfdc08451d00%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FGettyImages-489974606.jpg&h=17c637be&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"回憶小子走得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b2a88a3f9a15c92da2e31e0238162ec806de7f","tid":2372871,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"拜登班幕僚會唔會覺得自己白做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓又出埋都求唔到一官半職<br />\nCondom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19b48e52e9af9bbddafdebb66d3c69a7eaf3a40","tid":2372871,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}